Steve Smith became a self-made multi-millionaire with birth of Poundland . 
 52-year-old started life in business on his parents' Saturday market stall . 
 He opened first Poundland shop in 1990 when he was just 18-years-old . 
 Sold the firm for £50million in 2000 and gave half the profits to his parents . 
 Despite his wealth, his wife Tracy gives him '£10 - £20 pocket money daily'